productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Nauru and I bought one.
This Nevada, does exactly what it's suppose to do.
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
My neighbor Elisha has one of these. She works as a fortune teller and she says it looks floppy.
I saw one of these in Spratly Islands and I bought one.
